#: ../components/pro/gpa.rst:4
msgid ""
"This document describes how to use Gnu Privacy Assistant (GPA) to set up "
"the Nitrokey for its first usage."
msgstr ""
"Dit document beschrijft hoe je Gnu Privacy Assistant (GPA) kunt gebruiken"
