"*Operational* of *Locked*."

#: ../components/nethsm/administration.rst:112
msgid "*Operational*"
msgstr "*Operationeel"

#: ../components/nethsm/administration.rst:112
msgid ""
"NetHSM with configuration and ready to execute commands. The "
"*Operational* state implies the *Provisioned* state."
msgstr ""
"NetHSM met configuratie en klaar om commando's uit te voeren. De status "
"*Operational* impliceert de status *Provisioned*."

#: ../components/nethsm/administration.rst:115
msgid "*Locked*"
msgstr "*Vergrendeld*"

#: ../components/nethsm/administration.rst:115
msgid ""
